sentences.english: It was the site of a British victory over the Saxons in571. Population, 74, 500.

sentences.chinese: 阿尔比恩英格兰或大不列颠。

sentences.english: Hadrian's Wall is built across Britannia to keep out the barbarians .

sentences.english: Ben Nevis (1343m) the highest mountain in Britain is located in Scotland.
sentences.chinese: 位于苏格兰的本尼威斯山是大不列颠的最高山。

sentences.english: Great Britain has only two sleeper trains.
sentences.chinese: 大不列颠只有两条卧铺列车线路，都是快客。

sentences.english: Many of London's streets help narrate British history.

sentences.english: The coronation of King George I of Great Britain and Ireland took place.

sentences.english: Triumph, my Britain, thou hast one to show.

sentences.english: So there you go. "Appropriate and proportionate", as is the British way.

sentences.english: You've got Britain which is those same things.
sentences.chinese: 你听到的大不列颠帝国也是一样。
